title: Pregnant Kim K. Goes Makeup—and Heels—Free!
text: At eight months pregnant, Kim Kardashian has finally let go of her glamorous look. And she's still just as gorgeous. The expectant E! star was spotted in Malibu Tuesday, where she was snapped sans makeup at The Vitamin Barn with brother Brandon Jenner and his wife, Leah Felder. Kanye West's other half looked relaxed and casual in comfy black leggings, flip-flops and a black zip-up jacket. She flaunted her flawless fresh face and her very pregnant belly, sporting a tight black top that flatters her bump. PHOTO: Kim K Instagrams chic maternity look It's no secret Kim has been keeping up with her workouts throughout her pregnancy, and she took to Twitter Monday to share how she recently got her namaste on. "Tried yoga today. Was very relaxing," the brunette beauty wrote. "I was into it! Think I will try it again!" Nothing like a little deep breathing and relaxing to help prepare for her daughter's birth! Don't forget to tune in to Keeping Up With the Kardashians this week at 9 p.m. only on E!
